## 授权模式
### 授权码 Authorization Code

###发起请求
GET {{host}}/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id={{clientid}}&client_secret={{clientsecret}}&redirect_uri={{redirect_uri}}

###换取令牌
POST {{host}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic {{clientid}} {{clientsecret}}

grant_type=authorization_code&redirect_uri={{redirect_uri}}&code=0y1akY


### 隐式许可 Implicit
## 发起请求
GET {{host}}/oauth/authorize?response_type=token&client_id={{clientid}}&client_secret={{clientsecret}}&redirect_uri={{redirect_uri}}


